QuestData.Title: Trouble at the Overwatch
QuestData.Description: Ya know, we sent a couple o' scouts ta check out those big, smelly, 'civilized' ogres at Mar'gok's Overwatch.$B$BHaven't heard from 'em in a bit. Matter o' fact, not since I saved yer bacon up at Telaar.$B$BHave some time ta ride over there and check up on 'em, $g boyo:girly;?
QuestData.LogDescription: Locate Rangari Eleena at Mar'gok's Overwatch.
QuestData.RewardText: I'm afraid we have some trouble.
